  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this randomized clinical trial is to clinically evaluate the effectiveness of the
      adjunctive use of photodynamic therapy (PDT) with an light-emitting diode (LED) light source
      in the treatment of chronic periodontitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
