  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. clinically diagnosis of advanced chronic periodontitis with more than 3 mm clinical
             attachment loss

          2. presence of at least two teeth with probing depth of 4 to 6 mm without furcation
             involvement in each quadrant

          3. at least 16 remaining teeth

          4. no periodontal treatment in the past 12 months

          5. no evidence of systemic disease related to periodontal problems

          6. no use of antibiotics for the past 6 months

          7. No smoking more than 10 cigarettes per day

          8. no addiction to any kind of drugs

          9. no pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
